# Copilot runtime + SDK override for the product build.
#
# Overrides the `@github/copilot` (runtime) and `@github/copilot-sdk` packages
# VS Code depends on, without editing package.json by hand — analogous to the
# electron `target=` pin in .npmrc. A normal build leaves both values empty.
#
# Each value is one of:
#   - empty       -> no override (use the version pinned in package.json)
#   - <npm-spec>  -> a published version/range/dist-tag, e.g. 1.2.3, ^1.2.0, latest
#   - git:<ref>   -> build from source at a branch/tag/commit (TypeScript-only),
#                    e.g. git:main, git:my-branch, git:0a1b2c3
sdk=
runtime=
